                     <interp inst="t18430403-1116-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="forgery"></interp> for feloniously forging and uttering, on the <rs id="t18430403-cd-9" type="crimeDate">
                        <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18430403-1116-offence-1 t18430403-cd-9"></join>12th of October</rs>, a forged acquittance and receipt for 16<hi rend="italic">s</hi>., with intent to defraud <persName id="t18430403-name-139" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18430403-name-139" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18430403-name-139" type="surname" value="MARSHALL"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18430403-name-139" type="given" value="BENJAMIN CROSBY"></interp>
